<header class="church-hero">
  <div class="page-width church-hero__grid">
    <div class="church-hero__copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">The Bible Band™ for ministry</span>
      <h1 class="display-title">Put the Word <em>within reach.</em></h1>
      <p>Give your church, camp, youth group, school, retreat, or ministry team a shared daily rhythm of Scripture, a pastor-written devotion, guided prayer, and audio—all with one tap.</p>
      <div class="church-hero__actions">
        <a class="button button--gold" href="/pages/contact">Request bulk pricing</a>
        <a class="church-text-link" href="#church-how-it-works">See how it works <span aria-hidden="true">↓</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <aside class="church-hero__visual" aria-label="The Bible Band for churches">
      {% if section.settings.hero_image != blank %}
        {{ section.settings.hero_image | image_url: width: 1200 | image_tag: widths: '480, 720, 960, 1200', fetchpriority: 'high', alt: section.settings.hero_image.alt | default: 'Bible Bands ready for a church group' }}
      {% else %}
        <div class="church-hero__callout">
          <p class="church-hero__kicker">One tap. Every day.</p>
          <strong>No app.<br>No account.<br>No subscription.</strong>
          <span>Just a compatible smartphone and a willing heart.</span>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="church-hero__stamp"><strong>365</strong><span>days of<br>discipleship</span></div>
    </aside>
  </div>
  <div class="church-marquee" aria-hidden="true">
    <div>Scripture <b>✦</b> Devotion <b>✦</b> Prayer <b>✦</b> Audio <b>✦</b> One-Year Reading Plan <b>✦</b></div>
  </div>
</header>

<nav class="church-jump" aria-label="Church page sections">
  <div class="page-width church-jump__inner">
    <span>Explore the program</span>
    <a href="#church-who">Who it’s for</a>
    <a href="#church-how-it-works">How it works</a>
    <a href="#church-hub">Church hub</a>
    <a href="#church-faq">Questions</a>
    <a class="church-jump__cta" href="#church-inquiry">Plan your group</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="church-intro page-width">
  <div class="church-intro__heading">
    <span class="eyebrow">Made to be shared</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">One daily starting point. Countless conversations.</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="church-intro__copy">
    <p>The Bible Band™ makes it simple for everyone in your group to return to the same Scripture—at the gathering, around the dinner table, or throughout the week.</p>
    <div class="church-stat"><strong>365</strong><span>days of Scripture and guided devotion</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="church-sample">
  <div class="page-width church-sample__grid">
    <div class="church-sample__copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">See a real day</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">This is what one tap opens.</h2>
      <p>Every day begins with Scripture, a pastor-written devotion, guided prayer, audio, and a clear reading plan—all in one calm, focused place.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><span aria-hidden="true">01</span>Today’s Scripture</li>
        <li><span aria-hidden="true">02</span>Devotion &amp; guided prayer</li>
        <li><span aria-hidden="true">03</span>Audio &amp; daily readings</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="button button--gold" href="https://thebibleband.com/today" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open today’s experience <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
    </div>
    <a class="church-sample__screen" href="https://thebibleband.com/today" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Open a live sample day on The Bible Band">
      <span class="church-sample__bar"><i></i><i></i><i></i><b>thebibleband.com/today</b></span>
      <img src="{{ 'bible-band-sample-day.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Sample Bible Band daily experience showing the day’s Scripture from Matthew 11" width="1280" height="720" loading="lazy">
      <span class="church-sample__caption">Live daily content <b>View today ↗</b></span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="church-use-section" id="church-who">
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="church-section-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Built for real ministry</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Meet people where they are.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="church-use-grid">
      <article class="church-use-card church-use-card--rust"><span class="church-use-card__number">01</span><h3>Youth &amp; Students</h3><p>A simple, screen-native invitation to build a daily habit beyond Wednesday night.</p><span class="church-use-card__tag">Youth groups · VBS · Graduates</span></article>
      <article class="church-use-card church-use-card--gold"><span class="church-use-card__number">02</span><h3>Small Groups</h3><p>Start every gathering from common ground, then carry the conversation into the week.</p><span class="church-use-card__tag">Discipleship · Men · Women</span></article>
      <article class="church-use-card church-use-card--ink"><span class="church-use-card__number">03</span><h3>Outreach</h3><p>Offer a meaningful next step that is approachable for a visitor or brand-new believer.</p><span class="church-use-card__tag">Missions · Evangelism · Care</span></article>
      <article class="church-use-card church-use-card--cream"><span class="church-use-card__number">04</span><h3>Camps &amp; Retreats</h3><p>Carry the theme beyond the session with camp devotions, prayer prompts, schedules, and next steps.</p><span class="church-use-card__tag">Summer camp · Retreats · Conferences</span></article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="church-steps dark-section" id="church-how-it-works">
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="church-section-head church-section-head--split">
      <div><span class="eyebrow">Simple by design</span><h2 class="section-title">From wrist to Word in seconds.</h2></div>
      <p>No setup meeting. No passwords to remember. If they can unlock their phone and tap the band, they’re ready.</p>
    </div>
    <ol class="church-step-list">
      <li><span>1</span><div><h3>Wear it</h3><p>Keep a daily reminder of God’s Word close at hand.</p></div></li>
      <li><span>2</span><div><h3>Tap it</h3><p>Hold the band near a compatible smartphone.</p></div></li>
      <li><span>3</span><div><h3>Live it</h3><p>Read, listen, reflect, and pray—together or apart.</p></div></li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="church-hub" id="church-hub">
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="church-section-head church-section-head--split church-hub__head">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">One band. One church hub.</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">More ways to keep your church connected.</h2>
      </div>
      <p>The tap can become a familiar front door to what matters this week—from a focused prayer journey to the practical next step after Sunday service.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="church-hub__layout">
      <article class="church-prayer-card">
        <div class="church-prayer-card__top">
          <span>Featured ministry rhythm</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">21</span>
        </div>
        <div class="church-prayer-card__body">
          <p class="church-prayer-card__days">21 Days</p>
          <h3>Of Prayer</h3>
          <p>Invite the whole church into a shared daily practice with a prayer focus, Scripture, guided prompt, and audio encouragement available in one tap.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="church-prayer-card__progress" aria-label="Twenty-one days of prayer">
          {% for day in (1..21) %}<span{% if day <= 7 %} class="is-active"{% endif %}></span>{% endfor %}
        </div>
      </article>

      <div class="church-hub__links" aria-label="Church tap destinations">
        <article class="church-hub-link">
          <span class="church-hub-link__icon" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
          <div><span class="church-hub-link__label">This week</span><h3>Digital Bulletin</h3><p>Put announcements, service details, and important links within reach—without another handout.</p></div>
          <span class="church-hub-link__arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
        </article>
        <article class="church-hub-link">
          <span class="church-hub-link__icon" aria-hidden="true">✎</span>
          <div><span class="church-hub-link__label">Go deeper</span><h3>Sermon Notes</h3><p>Help people follow along, revisit the message, and carry one clear takeaway into the week.</p></div>
          <span class="church-hub-link__arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
        </article>
        <article class="church-hub-link">
          <span class="church-hub-link__icon" aria-hidden="true">$</span>
          <div><span class="church-hub-link__label">Tap to give</span><h3>Offering</h3><p>Make generosity easy to find by linking directly to your church’s secure giving page.</p></div>
          <span class="church-hub-link__arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
        </article>
        <article class="church-hub-link">
          <span class="church-hub-link__icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
          <div><span class="church-hub-link__label">Take a next step</span><h3>Events &amp; Connect</h3><p>Share registrations, prayer requests, newcomer information, groups, and upcoming events.</p></div>
          <span class="church-hub-link__arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="church-hub__note">
      <strong>Think of it as a living link.</strong>
      <p>Keep the band the same while the destination stays useful through changing seasons, campaigns, and ministry moments.</p>
      <a href="{{ section.settings.contact_link | default: '/pages/contact' }}">Talk through your church’s use case <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="church-package">
  <div class="page-width church-package__grid">
    <div class="church-package__intro">
      <span class="eyebrow">A simple ministry tool</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">The band is the invitation. The daily rhythm is the impact.</h2>
      <p>Give people something tangible to wear and one clear place to return each day. We’ll help you shape the experience around your ministry moment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="church-package__board">
      <div class="church-package__label">Your group rollout</div>
      <ol>
        <li><span>01</span><div><strong>Choose the moment</strong><p>Launch at a retreat, student night, prayer emphasis, welcome event, or church-wide initiative.</p></div></li>
        <li><span>02</span><div><strong>Choose the group</strong><p>Tell us who you’re equipping and roughly how many people you hope to reach.</p></div></li>
        <li><span>03</span><div><strong>Choose the destination</strong><p>Use the daily Bible Band experience or talk with us about a focused church hub.</p></div></li>
      </ol>
      <a class="church-package__link" href="#church-inquiry">Start planning <span aria-hidden="true">↘</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="church-scripture">
  <div class="page-width church-scripture__grid">
    <span class="church-scripture__mark" aria-hidden="true">11:18</span>
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">The idea behind the band</span>
      <blockquote>“Fix these words of mine in your hearts and minds; tie them as symbols on your hands.”</blockquote>
      <cite>Deuteronomy 11:18</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="church-trust page-width">
  <div class="church-trust__title"><span class="eyebrow">Why leaders choose it</span><h2 class="section-title">Low friction.<br>Lasting purpose.</h2></div>
  <ul class="church-checklist">
    <li><span aria-hidden="true">✓</span><strong>Ready out of the box</strong><p>No account, download, or subscription to manage.</p></li>
    <li><span aria-hidden="true">✓</span><strong>For teens and adults</strong><p>Approachable daily content for a wide range of groups.</p></li>
    <li><span aria-hidden="true">✓</span><strong>One shared rhythm</strong><p>Everyone receives the same daily Scripture and prompt.</p></li>
    <li><span aria-hidden="true">✓</span><strong>Made to travel</strong><p>Works worldwide with compatible smartphones.</p></li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="church-faq" id="church-faq">
  <div class="page-width church-faq__grid">
    <div><span class="eyebrow">Good questions</span><h2 class="section-title">Before you bring it to your group.</h2></div>
    <div class="church-faq__list">
      <details><summary>Does everyone need to download an app?</summary><p>No. A compatible smartphone opens the experience with a tap—there is no app, account, or subscription required.</p></details>
      <details><summary>Can one band serve different ministry moments?</summary><p>Yes. The band stays the same while the linked destination can remain useful through prayer initiatives, events, sermon series, and seasonal campaigns.</p></details>
      <details><summary>Can you help us choose the right rollout?</summary><p>Absolutely. Share your group, timing, and goals below. We’ll help you think through quantity, group pricing, and the simplest way to launch.</p></details>
      <details><summary>What phones are compatible?</summary><p>The Bible Band works with compatible iPhone and Android devices. A QR code backup is included for easy access when tapping is unavailable.</p></details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="church-bulk" id="church-inquiry">
  <div class="page-width church-bulk__inner">
    <div class="church-bulk__lead"><span class="eyebrow">Let’s equip your people</span><h2 class="display-title">Tell us about your group.</h2><p>Share the basics. We’ll follow up personally with the clearest next step for your church, camp, school, or ministry.</p><div class="church-response"><span aria-hidden="true">✦</span><p><strong>A real conversation.</strong><br>No generic sales funnel—just practical help shaping the right rollout.</p></div></div>
    <div class="church-inquiry-card">
      {% form 'contact' %}
        {% if form.posted_successfully? %}<p class="church-form-success" role="status">Thank you. We’ll be in touch soon to help plan your group.</p>{% endif %}
        {{ form.errors | default_errors }}
        <input type="hidden" name="contact[Subject]" value="Church and group pricing inquiry">
        <div class="church-field-grid">
          <div><label for="ChurchName-{{ section.id }}">Name</label><input id="ChurchName-{{ section.id }}" type="text" name="contact[name]" autocomplete="name" required></div>
          <div><label for="ChurchEmail-{{ section.id }}">Email</label><input id="ChurchEmail-{{ section.id }}" type="email" name="contact[email]" autocomplete="email" required></div>
        </div>
        <div><label for="ChurchOrganization-{{ section.id }}">Church or organization</label><input id="ChurchOrganization-{{ section.id }}" type="text" name="contact[Organization]" autocomplete="organization" required></div>
        <div class="church-field-grid">
          <div><label for="ChurchGroup-{{ section.id }}">Group type</label><select id="ChurchGroup-{{ section.id }}" name="contact[Group type]"><option>Church-wide</option><option>Students / youth</option><option>Small group</option><option>Camp / retreat</option><option>School</option><option>Outreach / missions</option><option>Other ministry</option></select></div>
          <div><label for="ChurchQuantity-{{ section.id }}">Estimated quantity</label><input id="ChurchQuantity-{{ section.id }}" type="number" name="contact[Estimated quantity]" min="1" inputmode="numeric" placeholder="About how many?"></div>
        </div>
        <div><label for="ChurchMessage-{{ section.id }}">What are you planning?</label><textarea id="ChurchMessage-{{ section.id }}" name="contact[body]" rows="4" placeholder="Tell us about your event, timing, or ministry goal."></textarea></div>
        <button class="button button--gold" type="submit">Request group pricing</button>
        <p class="church-form-note">Prefer email? <a href="{{ section.settings.contact_link | default: '/pages/contact' }}">Use our general contact page</a>.</p>
      {% endform %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% stylesheet %}
  .church-hero{overflow:hidden;border-bottom:2px solid var(--ink)}
  .church-hero__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1.35fr) minmax(280px,.65fr);gap:clamp(40px,7vw,110px);align-items:center;padding-block:clamp(70px,9vw,130px)}
  .church-hero .display-title{max-width:950px;font-size:clamp(54px,8.2vw,126px)}
  .church-hero .display-title em{display:block;color:var(--rust);font-style:normal}
  .church-hero__copy>p{max-width:680px;margin:32px 0 0;color:var(--brown);font-size:clamp(17px,1.6vw,21px);line-height:1.65}
  .church-hero__actions{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;gap:22px;margin-top:34px}
  .church-text-link{font-size:12px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;text-underline-offset:5px}
  .church-hero__visual{position:relative;min-width:0}.church-hero__visual>img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/5;object-fit:cover;border:2px solid var(--ink);box-shadow:18px 18px 0 var(--gold);transform:rotate(1.5deg)}
  .church-hero__callout{position:relative;padding:38px 34px 34px;background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream);box-shadow:18px 18px 0 var(--gold);transform:rotate(1.5deg)}
  .church-hero__callout::before{content:"✦";position:absolute;right:22px;top:18px;color:var(--gold);font-size:28px}
  .church-hero__kicker{margin:0 0 24px;color:var(--gold);font-size:11px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase}
  .church-hero__callout strong{display:block;font-size:clamp(28px,3vw,43px);line-height:1.05;text-transform:uppercase}
  .church-hero__callout>span{display:block;margin-top:24px;color:#c9c4bc;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}
  .church-hero__stamp{position:absolute;right:-18px;bottom:-30px;display:flex;width:126px;height:126px;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;border:2px solid var(--ink);border-radius:50%;background:var(--rust);color:var(--cream);text-align:center;transform:rotate(-8deg)}.church-hero__stamp strong{font-size:42px;line-height:.9}.church-hero__stamp span{margin-top:7px;font-size:9px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.2px;line-height:1.15;text-transform:uppercase}
  .church-marquee{overflow:hidden;padding:14px 0;background:var(--rust);color:var(--cream);font-size:12px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-align:center;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap}
  .church-marquee div{min-width:max-content}.church-marquee b{margin:0 22px;color:var(--gold)}
  .church-jump{position:sticky;top:84px;z-index:20;border-bottom:2px solid var(--ink);background:rgba(244,236,226,.96);backdrop-filter:blur(10px)}.church-jump__inner{display:flex;min-height:54px;align-items:center;gap:clamp(16px,2.5vw,38px);overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:none}.church-jump__inner::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}.church-jump span,.church-jump a{flex:0 0 auto;font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.2px;text-decoration:none;text-transform:uppercase}.church-jump>div>span{color:var(--rust)}.church-jump__cta{margin-left:auto;padding:9px 13px;background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream)}
  .church-intro{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr .8fr;gap:clamp(40px,9vw,140px);align-items:end;padding-block:clamp(70px,9vw,120px)}
  .church-intro__copy>p{margin:0;color:var(--brown);font-size:17px;line-height:1.75}
  .church-stat{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px;margin-top:30px;padding-top:22px;border-top:2px solid var(--ink)}
  .church-stat strong{color:var(--rust);font-size:50px;line-height:1}.church-stat span{max-width:180px;font-size:12px;font-weight:850;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}
  .church-sample{padding:clamp(80px,10vw,140px) 0;background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream);overflow:hidden}.church-sample__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(280px,.7fr) minmax(0,1.3fr);gap:clamp(45px,7vw,100px);align-items:center}.church-sample .eyebrow{color:var(--gold)}.church-sample__copy>p{max-width:560px;margin:26px 0;color:#c9c4bc;font-size:17px;line-height:1.7}.church-sample__copy ul{margin:0 0 32px;padding:0;list-style:none;border-top:1px solid #4e473e}.church-sample__copy li{display:grid;grid-template-columns:42px 1fr;gap:12px;padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #4e473e;font-size:12px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase}.church-sample__copy li span{color:var(--gold);font-size:10px}.church-sample__copy .button span{margin-left:10px;font-size:17px}.church-sample__screen{display:block;min-width:0;border:2px solid var(--cream);background:#eee9df;color:var(--ink);box-shadow:14px 14px 0 var(--rust);text-decoration:none;transform:rotate(1deg);transition:transform .2s}.church-sample__screen:hover{transform:rotate(0) translateY(-4px)}.church-sample__bar{display:flex;height:40px;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:0 14px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--ink);background:var(--cream)}.church-sample__bar i{width:9px;height:9px;border:1px solid var(--ink);border-radius:50%}.church-sample__bar i:first-child{background:var(--rust)}.church-sample__bar b{margin-left:8px;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px}.church-sample__screen img{width:100%;height:auto}.church-sample__caption{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 18px;border-top:2px solid var(--ink);font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.2px;text-transform:uppercase}.church-sample__caption b{color:var(--rust)}
  .church-use-section{padding:clamp(70px,8vw,110px) 0;background:#e4d4bf}
  .church-section-head{max-width:820px;margin-bottom:42px}.church-use-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:18px}
  .church-use-card{min-height:310px;padding:34px;border:2px solid var(--ink);display:flex;flex-direction:column;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s}
  .church-use-card:hover{transform:translate(-4px,-4px);box-shadow:8px 8px 0 var(--ink)}
  .church-use-card--rust{background:var(--rust);color:var(--cream)}.church-use-card--gold{background:var(--gold)}.church-use-card--ink{background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream)}.church-use-card--cream{background:var(--cream)}
  .church-use-card__number{font-size:12px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:2px}.church-use-card h3{margin:auto 0 12px;font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,52px);line-height:.95;text-transform:uppercase}.church-use-card p{max-width:520px;margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6}.church-use-card__tag{padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid currentColor;font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.4px;text-transform:uppercase}
  .church-section-head--split{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;gap:70px;max-width:none;align-items:end}.church-section-head--split>p{margin:0;color:#c9c4bc;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7}
  .church-step-list{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);margin:50px 0 0;padding:0;list-style:none;border-top:1px solid #4e473e}
  .church-step-list li{display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;gap:20px;padding:34px 30px 10px 0;border-right:1px solid #4e473e}.church-step-list li+li{padding-left:30px}.church-step-list li:last-child{border-right:0}
  .church-step-list li>span{display:flex;width:44px;height:44px;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border:2px solid var(--gold);border-radius:50%;color:var(--gold);font-weight:900}.church-step-list h3{margin:8px 0 10px;font-size:24px;text-transform:uppercase}.church-step-list p{margin:0;color:#c9c4bc;line-height:1.6}
  .church-hub{padding:clamp(80px,10vw,140px) 0;background:var(--cream)}
  .church-hub__head>p{color:var(--brown)}
  .church-hub__layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(300px,.78fr) minmax(0,1.22fr);gap:18px;align-items:stretch}
  .church-prayer-card{display:flex;min-height:630px;flex-direction:column;padding:34px;background:var(--gold);border:2px solid var(--ink);box-shadow:10px 10px 0 var(--rust)}
  .church-prayer-card__top{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
  .church-prayer-card__top span:last-child{display:flex;width:48px;height:48px;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border:2px solid var(--ink);border-radius:50%;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0}
  .church-prayer-card__body{margin:auto 0}.church-prayer-card__days{margin:0;font-size:clamp(26px,3vw,42px);font-weight:950;line-height:1;text-transform:uppercase}.church-prayer-card h3{margin:0 0 24px;font-size:clamp(58px,7vw,102px);letter-spacing:-.06em;line-height:.78;text-transform:uppercase}.church-prayer-card__body>p:last-child{max-width:480px;margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.65}
  .church-prayer-card__progress{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:7px;padding-top:25px;border-top:2px solid var(--ink)}.church-prayer-card__progress span{aspect-ratio:1;border:1px solid var(--ink);border-radius:50%}.church-prayer-card__progress .is-active{background:var(--rust)}
  .church-hub__links{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:18px}
  .church-hub-link{position:relative;display:grid;grid-template-columns:52px 1fr auto;gap:18px;min-height:306px;padding:28px;border:2px solid var(--ink);background:#e4d4bf;transition:background .2s,color .2s,transform .2s}
  .church-hub-link:nth-child(2),.church-hub-link:nth-child(3){background:var(--cream)}.church-hub-link:hover{background:var(--rust);color:var(--cream);transform:translateY(-4px)}.church-hub-link:hover p{color:var(--cream)}
  .church-hub-link__icon{display:flex;width:52px;height:52px;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border:2px solid currentColor;border-radius:50%;font-size:18px;font-weight:950}
  .church-hub-link__label{display:block;margin:6px 0 18px;color:var(--rust);font-size:9px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.4px;text-transform:uppercase}.church-hub-link:hover .church-hub-link__label{color:var(--gold)}
  .church-hub-link h3{margin:auto 0 12px;font-size:clamp(25px,3vw,39px);line-height:.95;text-transform:uppercase}.church-hub-link p{margin:0;color:var(--brown);font-size:13px;line-height:1.55}.church-hub-link__arrow{font-size:24px}
  .church-hub__note{display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto;gap:28px;align-items:center;margin-top:28px;padding:22px 0;border-block:2px solid var(--ink)}.church-hub__note strong{font-size:16px;text-transform:uppercase}.church-hub__note p{margin:0;color:var(--brown);font-size:14px;line-height:1.5}.church-hub__note a{font-size:11px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;text-underline-offset:4px;white-space:nowrap}
  .church-package{padding:clamp(80px,10vw,140px) 0;background:#e4d4bf;border-block:2px solid var(--ink)}.church-package__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:.82fr 1.18fr;gap:clamp(45px,8vw,120px);align-items:start}.church-package__intro{position:sticky;top:170px}.church-package__intro>p{max-width:580px;margin:28px 0 0;color:var(--brown);font-size:17px;line-height:1.7}.church-package__board{border:2px solid var(--ink);background:var(--cream);box-shadow:12px 12px 0 var(--rust)}.church-package__label{padding:18px 24px;border-bottom:2px solid var(--ink);color:var(--rust);font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase}.church-package__board ol{margin:0;padding:0 28px;list-style:none}.church-package__board li{display:grid;grid-template-columns:62px 1fr;gap:20px;padding:28px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #cfc2b1}.church-package__board li>span{color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px var(--rust);font-size:38px;font-weight:950;line-height:1}.church-package__board strong{font-size:17px;text-transform:uppercase}.church-package__board p{margin:8px 0 0;color:var(--brown);font-size:14px;line-height:1.55}.church-package__link{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:22px 28px;background:var(--gold);font-size:11px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-decoration:none;text-transform:uppercase}.church-package__link span{font-size:20px}
  .church-scripture{padding:clamp(80px,10vw,150px) 0;background:var(--rust);color:var(--cream)}
  .church-scripture__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:.55fr 1.45fr;gap:50px;align-items:start}.church-scripture__mark{color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:2px var(--gold);font-size:clamp(72px,12vw,180px);font-weight:950;letter-spacing:-.08em;line-height:.75}.church-scripture .eyebrow{color:var(--gold)}.church-scripture blockquote{max-width:900px;margin:18px 0 26px;font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,70px);font-weight:950;letter-spacing:-.045em;line-height:1.05}.church-scripture cite{font-size:11px;font-style:normal;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase}
  .church-trust{display:grid;grid-template-columns:.8fr 1.2fr;gap:clamp(50px,9vw,140px);padding-block:clamp(80px,10vw,140px)}.church-checklist{margin:0;padding:0;list-style:none}.church-checklist li{display:grid;grid-template-columns:38px 1fr;gap:2px 16px;padding:20px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--ink)}.church-checklist li:last-child{border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink)}.church-checklist li>span{grid-row:1/3;color:var(--rust);font-size:26px}.church-checklist strong{font-size:17px;text-transform:uppercase}.church-checklist p{margin:5px 0 0;color:var(--brown);line-height:1.55}
  .church-faq{padding:clamp(80px,10vw,140px) 0;background:var(--cream);border-top:2px solid var(--ink)}.church-faq__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:.8fr 1.2fr;gap:clamp(50px,9vw,140px)}.church-faq__list details{border-top:1px solid var(--ink)}.church-faq__list details:last-child{border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink)}.church-faq__list summary{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:24px;padding:24px 0;cursor:pointer;list-style:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:900;text-transform:uppercase}.church-faq__list summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}.church-faq__list summary::after{content:"+";color:var(--rust);font-size:24px;font-weight:400}.church-faq__list details[open] summary::after{content:"−"}.church-faq__list details p{max-width:700px;margin:-6px 0 24px;color:var(--brown);line-height:1.65}
  .church-bulk{padding:clamp(80px,10vw,140px) 0;background:var(--ink);color:var(--cream)}.church-bulk__inner{display:grid;grid-template-columns:.9fr 1.1fr;gap:clamp(50px,8vw,120px);align-items:start}.church-bulk .display-title{font-size:clamp(50px,7vw,105px)}.church-bulk .eyebrow{color:var(--gold)}.church-bulk__lead>p{max-width:620px;color:#c9c4bc;font-size:17px;line-height:1.7}.church-response{display:flex;gap:16px;margin-top:34px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid #4e473e}.church-response>span{color:var(--gold);font-size:24px}.church-response p{margin:0;color:#c9c4bc;font-size:13px;line-height:1.55}.church-response strong{color:var(--cream);text-transform:uppercase}.church-inquiry-card{padding:clamp(24px,4vw,42px);border:2px solid var(--cream);background:var(--cream);color:var(--ink);box-shadow:12px 12px 0 var(--rust)}.church-inquiry-card form{display:grid;gap:18px}.church-field-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px}.church-inquiry-card label{display:block;margin-bottom:7px;font-size:10px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:1.4px;text-transform:uppercase}.church-inquiry-card input,.church-inquiry-card select,.church-inquiry-card textarea{width:100%;padding:13px;border:1px solid var(--ink);background:#f4ece2;color:var(--ink);font:inherit}.church-inquiry-card textarea{resize:vertical}.church-inquiry-card .button{width:100%}.church-form-success{margin:0;padding:16px;background:#dce8d2;border:1px solid var(--ink);font-weight:800;line-height:1.5}.church-form-note{margin:0;color:var(--brown);font-size:11px;text-align:center}.church-form-note a{text-underline-offset:3px}.church-inquiry-card .errors{margin:0;padding:14px 14px 14px 32px;background:#f1d3c7}
  @media(max-width:900px){.church-hero__grid,.church-intro,.church-sample__grid,.church-section-head--split,.church-hub__layout,.church-package__grid,.church-scripture__grid,.church-trust,.church-faq__grid,.church-bulk__inner{grid-template-columns:1fr}.church-hero__visual{max-width:500px}.church-sample__screen{margin-right:14px}.church-package__intro{position:static}.church-step-list{grid-template-columns:1fr}.church-step-list li,.church-step-list li+li{padding:26px 0;border-right:0;border-bottom:1px solid #4e473e}.church-prayer-card{min-height:540px}.church-scripture__mark{font-size:90px}.church-bulk__lead{max-width:680px}.church-hub__note{grid-template-columns:1fr}.church-hub__note a{white-space:normal}.church-jump{top:68px}.church-jump>div>span{display:none}}
  @media(max-width:640px){.church-hero__grid{padding-block:55px 78px}.church-hero__callout{margin-right:12px;padding:30px 26px}.church-hero__stamp{right:-5px;width:104px;height:104px}.church-hero__stamp strong{font-size:34px}.church-jump__inner{gap:20px}.church-jump__cta{margin-left:0}.church-use-grid,.church-hub__links,.church-field-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.church-use-card{min-height:270px;padding:26px}.church-intro{align-items:start}.church-stat strong{font-size:44px}.church-section-head--split{gap:22px}.church-prayer-card{min-height:500px;padding:26px}.church-hub-link{min-height:260px;padding:24px;grid-template-columns:46px 1fr auto}.church-hub-link__icon{width:46px;height:46px}.church-package__board li{grid-template-columns:48px 1fr;padding:24px 0}.church-package__board li>span{font-size:30px}.church-scripture__grid{gap:28px}.church-trust{gap:42px}.church-inquiry-card{margin-right:10px}.church-bulk__actions{align-items:stretch;flex-direction:column}.church-bulk__actions .button{width:100%}}
{% endstylesheet %}

